*&quot;Voodoo-U&quot; (1994)
*&quot;Our Little Secret&quot; (1997)
*&quot;Farstucker&quot; (2001)
*&quot;Deep Chills&quot; (2012)
*&quot;Pretty in Kink&quot; (2018)
*&quot;Acid Reign&quot; (TBA)

