*Michael Ancher (1996)
*Hans Christian Andersen (1935)
*Ib Andersen (1991)
*Mogens Andersen (1998)
*Valdemar Andersen (1991)
*Anne-Marie of Denmark Queen consort of Greece (1950 semi-postal)

